It took us two years.

1083
00:50:31,060 --> 00:50:33,795
[ Cheers and applause ]

1084
00:50:42,205 --> 00:50:43,238
Happy?

1085
00:50:44,240 --> 00:50:45,807
More than.

1086
00:50:45,809 --> 00:50:47,843
Perhaps now
they'll give us some peace.

1087
00:50:52,282 --> 00:50:53,949
[ Chuckles ]

1088
00:50:56,553 --> 00:50:57,686
Clerk: Enjoy the play.

1089
00:50:57,688 --> 00:50:59,221
Man: Thank you.

1090
00:50:59,223 --> 00:51:01,156
[ Indistinct conversations ]

1091
00:51:04,060 --> 00:51:06,628
Richard:
Where is my bloody wife?

