1160
00:54:41,478 --> 00:54:43,512
[ Cheers and applause ]

1161
00:54:43,514 --> 00:54:45,547
[ Up-tempo music playing ]

1162
00:54:53,790 --> 00:54:55,824
[ Applause ]

1163
00:54:55,826 --> 00:54:57,359
