1164
00:54:57,361 --> 00:54:59,828
Mm. That's easy for you to say.
You've already got one.

1165
00:54:59,830 --> 00:55:01,096
And I'm here
to make sure

1166
00:55:01,098 --> 00:55:02,931
you remember
that it means nothing.

1167
00:55:02,933 --> 00:55:06,802
I lost to Lee Marvin.

1168
00:55:06,804 --> 00:55:08,236
[ Both laugh ]

1169
00:55:08,238 --> 00:55:10,972
I mean, I love Lee,
but "Cat Ballou"?

1170
00:55:10,974 --> 00:55:12,974
He beat Rod and Olivier, too.

1171
00:55:12,976 --> 00:55:15,544
[ Sighs ]
It's a farce.

