00:55:19,583 --> 00:55:21,216
Don't patronize me.

1175
00:55:21,218 --> 00:55:23,218
I don't want yours.
I wanted <i>that</i> one.

1176
00:55:23,220 --> 00:55:24,853
I'm trying
to cheer you up.

1177
00:55:24,855 --> 00:55:25,854
Well, don't!

1178
00:55:25,856 --> 00:55:27,289
[ Sighs ]

1179
00:55:27,291 --> 00:55:28,957
Be a big sulk, then.

1180
00:55:28,959 --> 00:55:31,026
[ Sighs ]
Okay.

1181
00:55:31,028 --> 00:55:32,594
Be a big, pathetic,
sad sulk, then!

1182
00:55:32,596 --> 00:55:34,362
Damn it, woman,
can't you see that this hurts?!

1183
00:55:37,533 --> 00:55:40,035
No. No.

1184
00:55:40,037 --> 00:55:41,903
[ Sighs ]
Forgive me.

1185
00:55:43,940 --> 00:55:45,407
Please.

1186
00:55:48,477 --> 00:55:51,079
[ Cheers and applause ]

1187
00:55:55,507 --> 00:55:57,386
Oh, they give you the prize
years ago. m'dear.

