00:55:57,387 --> 00:56:00,223
There isn't an abomination award
you haven't won.

1189
00:56:00,287 --> 00:56:01,623
<i>Oh, God.</i>

1190
00:56:01,625 --> 00:56:03,491
[ Laughter ]

1191
00:56:03,493 --> 00:56:05,460
<i>- ...puke.</i>
<i>- What?</i>

1192
00:56:05,462 --> 00:56:07,128
<i>You make me puke!</i>

1193
00:56:07,130 --> 00:56:08,897
<i>Well, that wasn't</i>
<i>a very nice thing to say.</i>

1194
00:56:08,899 --> 00:56:10,866
You're fantastic.

1195
00:56:10,868 --> 00:56:12,968
Oh, thank you.

1196
00:56:12,970 --> 00:56:14,269
Yes, that's my gal --

1197
00:56:14,271 --> 00:56:16,638
the very essence
of a frumpy fishwife.

1198
00:56:16,640 --> 00:56:18,006
<i>...a simp.</i>

1199
00:56:18,008 --> 00:56:19,341
<i>You haven't even got...</i>

1200
00:56:19,343 --> 00:56:20,876
What about you?

1201
00:56:20,878 --> 00:56:22,944
You're castrated
and going to seed and tallow?

