1208
00:56:36,960 --> 00:56:39,060
I don't like it when you get
all of the attention?

1209
00:56:39,062 --> 00:56:41,162
Then why the hell
did I marry you?!

1210
00:56:41,164 --> 00:56:43,331
<i>I hope that was</i>
<i>an</i> empty <i>bottle, George.</i>

1211
00:56:43,333 --> 00:56:45,500
<i>You can't afford</i>
<i>to waste good liquor.</i>

1212
00:56:45,502 --> 00:56:50,906
- Prick.   - Elizabeth, you can stop.
The crowds aren't watching.

1213
00:56:50,908 --> 00:56:52,507
Like I care
who's watching!

1214
00:56:52,509 --> 00:56:54,509
Elizabeth, stop it!

1215
00:56:54,511 --> 00:56:56,111
This is not you!

1216
00:56:56,113 --> 00:56:58,680
Oh, yeah?

1217
00:56:58,682 --> 00:57:00,649
What's me?!

1218
00:57:02,451 --> 00:57:03,685
Is that me?!

1219
00:57:03,687 --> 00:57:05,086
Is that me?

1220
00:57:05,088 --> 00:57:06,321
[ Gasps ]

1221
00:57:06,323 --> 00:57:08,456
Oh, God.
