1233
00:57:38,989 --> 00:57:40,655
No, you wouldn't.

1234
00:57:40,657 --> 00:57:42,490
Try me.

1235
00:57:44,493 --> 00:57:47,062
[ Mariachi music playing ]

1236
00:57:47,064 --> 00:57:50,131
[ Telephone ringing ]

1237
00:57:54,070 --> 00:57:56,538
[ Ringing continues ]

1238
00:57:56,540 --> 00:57:58,573
[ Groans ]

1239
00:57:58,575 --> 00:58:00,709
All right, I'm coming.

1240
00:58:02,979 --> 00:58:04,346
Hello?

1241
00:58:08,484 --> 00:58:09,718
Are you sure?

1242
00:58:11,187 --> 00:58:13,021
Thank you.

1243
00:58:14,991 --> 00:58:16,658
[ Pan clattering ]
Wake up!

1244
00:58:16,660 --> 00:58:17,659
